ss=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setAttribute</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"country\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"usa\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\npersonElem2<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">appendChild</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>addressElem5<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\npeopleElem<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">appendChild</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>personElem1<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\npeopleElem<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">appendChild</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>personElem2<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\ndoc<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">appendChild</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>peopleElem<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>See also the <a href=\"/zh-CN/XUL_Tutorial/Document_Object_Model\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">DOM chapter of the XUL Tutorial</a>.</p>\n<p>You can automate the creation of a DOM tree using a <a href=\"/zh-CN/JXON#JXON_reverse_algorithms\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">JXON reverse algorithm</a> in association with the following JSON representation:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"people\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span clas